!!!
%html
  %head
    %link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css")
    %script{:src => "http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"}
    %script{:src => "http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.8.16/jquery-ui.min.js"}
    %script{:src => "/js/ui.js"}
    %script{:src => "/js/processing.min.js"} 

    %title app.net Neovigator

  %body
    %canvas#neoviz
    %header
      %section#title
        %h1 App.Net Neovigator
        %p Follow Graph Browser
      %section#search
        %form{:action => "/", :method => "get"}
          %label Username:
          %input#neoid{:type => "text", :value => "#{@user}", :name => "user"}
          %input#loadnode{:type => "submit", :value => "Load", :class => "button"}
      %br{:style => "clear: both;"}
    %section#content
      = yield
    %aside
      %div#explanation
        / Neovigator introduction
        %h2 About
        %p
          This Neo4j database contains the follows-relationships from 
          %a{:href => "https://alpha.app.net", :target=>"_blank"} app.net
        %p
          Neovigator is an attempt to visually navigate through 
          %a{:href => "http://neo4j.org"} Neo4j 
          by using the 
          %a{:href => "https://github.com/maxdemarzi/neography"} Neography
          Gem.
        %p
          It takes advantage of the latest HTML5 features
          by using the canvas element for drawing.
        %h3 Get started
        %p
          Start using the browser by just typing in the name of an app.net user.
          You can see the members at the 
          %a{:href => "https://alpha.app.net/global/", :target => "_blank" } global stream of app.net
          , try loading
          %a{:href => "/?user=stephenfry"} 
            %b Stephen Fry's
          node to get started.    
        %h3 Quirks
        %p
          There may be some unexpected behavior. Performance may drop significantly as
          the number of nodes increases.
        %h3 Credits
        %p
          This project was made by  
          %a{:href => "http://maxdemarzi.com"} Max De Marzi
          using: 
          %a{:href => "http://neo4j.org", :target => "_blank"} Neo4j
          and
          %a{:href => "https://github.com/maxdemarzi/neography", :target => "_blank"} Neography
          , it is based on 
          %a{:href => "http://askken.heroku.com/", :target => "_blank"} Ask Ken
          created by 
          %a{:href => "http://twitter.com/_mql", :target => "_blank"} Michael Aufreiter 
        %h3 Code          
        %p
          Available at
          %a{:href => "https://github.com/jexp/app-net", :target => "_blank"} Github    

